00:00:32.982 --> 00:00:34.141
In my view,

00:00:34.165 --> 00:00:36.974
capitalism should not
be thought of as an ideology,

00:00:36.998 --> 00:00:40.276
but instead should be thought of
as an operating system.

00:00:40.849 --> 00:00:42.117
Think of your iPhone.

00:00:42.762 --> 00:00:46.659
Your iPhone merges hardware with software.

00:00:46.683 --> 00:00:48.047
Apps and hardware.

00:00:48.071 --> 00:00:51.808
Now think about all the hardware
as the physical reality all around you,

00:00:51.832 --> 00:00:54.600
and think of the apps
as entrepreneurial activity,

00:00:54.624 --> 00:00:55.774
creative energy.

00:00:56.188 --> 00:00:58.863
And in-between,
you have an operating system.

